{"tid":1253842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"原來美國先賢已經教過香港人點做","createTime":"2019-06-23T19:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T00:01:27.000Z","uid":260806,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2dda24dff3e623128eadfb68456aab3093a4ee80","tid":1253842,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"美國《獨立宣言》雖然有正式嘅<strong>書面語版本</strong>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://web-archive-2017.ait.org.tw/zh/declaration-of-independence.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb-archive-2017.ait.org.tw%2Fzh%2Fdeclaration-of-independence.html&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=8de2faff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web-archive-2017.ait.org.tw/zh/declaration-of-independence.html</a><br />\n但係每次我發夢睇到以下嘅段落，我都覺得好似係講緊香港嘅處境。我喺夢遊嘅時候，嘗試用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廣東話</span></strong>演繹一次。我又發夢咁讀畀屋企人聽。佢哋發開口夢話，冇諗過，其實面對所謂「同文同種」嘅同胞，係可以有咁多委屈。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n我哋認爲好多道理唔需要講到明：人人平等、天賦人權<br />\n包括咗生命權、自由權同追求幸福嘅權利<br />\n人類爲咗保障呢啲權利先建立政府<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n慎重起見<br />\n做咗咁多年嘅政府<br />\n係唔應該因爲佢犯少少錯就廢咗佢<br />\n好多嘢只要仲可以忍<br />\n大家都會忍落去<br />\n從來唔會輕易就話推翻政府<br />\n但係如果政府<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持續濫權</span></strong><br />\n官員繼續巧取豪奪<br />\n人民繼續受到專制統治同鎮壓<br />\n人民不但有權亦有義務推翻政府<br />\n爲自己未來建立新嘅安全保障<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n每一次我哋都係好似請願咁<br />\n求個政府停止暴行<br />\n但每次都係繼續畀佢哋踐踏<br />\n如果個皇帝已經係一個暴君<br />\n佢就唔配繼續統治呢度嘅人民<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n我哋唔係冇顧念過祖國嘅同胞<br />\n我哋成日提醒佢哋<br />\n佢哋嘅立法機關成日將條法例塞落來我哋度<br />\n我哋都有表達過<br />\n我哋都曾經好天真咁相信佢哋有正義感<br />\n我哋求下佢哋念在同文同種嘅份上<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好成日來搶嘢</span></strong><br />\n大家好來好去咪算囉<br />\n但係佢哋對呢啲申訴當做耳邊風<br />\n冇辦法喇<br />\n我哋唯有劃清界線<br />\n從今之後我哋對佢哋就好似對世界上嘅其他人一樣<br />\n同我哋開拖嘅，就係敵人<br />\n同我哋 Friend 嘅，就係朋友<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹係歷史文學欣賞，請勿輕易對號入座。"},{"pid":"e4978b819d714408a734005d539684c633cfa892","tid":1253842,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceddfaa0a55e1b5375f30b4532c038830e2df06d","tid":1253842,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:57:51.000Z","msg":"大家要當係故事咁<br />\n講畀下一代聽"},{"pid":"23e4968187dd8379741e9a745adbd193295e507d","tid":1253842,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T20:23:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5afad5e252e5ec5507e61848a3bb8a19e7a1e5b5","tid":1253842,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T20:32:02.000Z","msg":"然後美國而家已經係the greatest country on earth"},{"pid":"a35b802eae5aafba66379c72353eb46e8d9cbc4b","tid":1253842,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T20:35:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"21ceabb5ce33728fd87f9bc030043bac5002ec94","tid":1253842,"uid":35668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T20:36:38.000Z","msg":"Boston Massacre<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb454d4d7459c128778a4f37cc0b0c11a8298762","tid":1253842,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T22:55:00.000Z","msg":"可以寫得再好D？"},{"pid":"1fd65d4587b66ecd0ef3536a0758a468fb63b225","tid":1253842,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:34:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9a281f82fc8ba1bcb8694f59881ba4c39546e161","tid":1253842,"uid":3326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:01:27.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}